94
00:05:59,701 --> 00:06:01,400
i onda ako ste stvarno dobri

95
00:06:01,401 --> 00:06:03,000
oni ce vam ponuditi posao

96
00:06:03,001 --> 00:06:06,100
Trecina Islandskih finansijskih regulatora

97
00:06:06,101 --> 00:06:09,000
je otišla da radi za banke

98
00:06:09,001 --> 00:06:12,300
Ali ovo je univerzalni problem,

99
