-Mislim da jesu

127
00:08:16,121 --> 00:08:19,000
Sef lobista
Okrugli sto finansijskih usluga

128
00:08:19,001 --> 00:08:22,000
I tako pomažete ovim ljudima da rasture svet?

129
00:08:22,001 --> 00:08:24,000
Možete i tako da kazete

130
00:08:33,000 --> 00:08:36,000
Imali su ogromne privatne dobitke
po osnovu javnog gubitka

131
00:08:36,766 --> 00:08:39,929
Glavni savetnik,
Bankarska Regulatorna Komisija Kine

132
00:08:45,000 --> 00:08:46,700
Kada pocnete da razmišljate da

133
00:08:46,701 --> 00:08:48,700
možete da napravite nešto ni iz cega

134
00:08:48,701 --> 00:08:50,000
veoma je teško odupreti se

135
00:08:50,113 --> 00:08:52,946
Premijer Singapura

136
00:09:04,000 --> 00:09:06,500
Brine me da mnogi ljudi

137
00:09:06,501 --> 00:09:08,000
žele da se vrate starim putem

138
00:09:08,001 --> 00:09:11,500
i rade kako su radili pre krize

139
00:09:12,009 --> 00:09:14,297
Ministarka Finansija Francuske

140
00:09:21,000 --> 00:09:24,400
dobijala sam anonimne e-mailove
od bankara

141
00:09:24,401 --> 00:09:26,400
gde kažu: "Nemojte da me citirate,

142
00:09:26,401 --> 00:09:28,400
ali ja sam stvarno zabrinut"

143
00:09:29,151 --> 00:09:31,733
Urednik
The Financial Times

144
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:35,000
Šta mislite zašto se ne preduzima

145
00:09:35,001 --> 00:09:38,500
dublja sistematska istraga?

146
00:09:38,501 --> 00:09:41,000
Zato što bi se tada otkrili krivci

147
00:09:41,001 --> 00:09:42,864
Profesor, NYU Business School

148
00:09:44,001 --> 00:09:45,500
Da li mislite da Columbia Business School

149
00:09:45,501 --> 00:09:49,000
ima znacajan sukob interesa?

150
00:09:49,000 --> 00:09:51,000
Ne vidim da mi...

151
00:09:51,001 --> 00:09:53,252
Glavni Bushov Ekonomski Savetnik
Dekan Columbia Business School

152
00:09:58,139 --> 00:10:00,000
Bivsi Guverner New Yorka
Bivsi Vrhovni Tuzilac New Yorka

153
00:10:00,001 --> 00:10:02,000
Regulatori nisu odradili njihov deo

154
00:10:02,001 --> 00:10:04,200
a imali su moc da ga odrade

155
00:10:04,201 --> 00:10:06,000
svaki slucaj koji sam uradio
kada sam bio vrhovni tužilac

156
00:10:06,001 --> 00:10:08,000
oni jednostavno nisu hteli

157
00:10:25,500 --> 00:10:27,800
Preko noci, Lehman Brothers
jedna od najcenjenijih

158
00:10:27,801 --> 00:10:30,800
i najvecih investicionih banaka,
je bila prisiljena da objavi bankrot

159
00:10:30,801 --> 00:10:33,500
još jedna, Merrill Lynch,
je prisiljena na prodaju danas

160
00:10:33,501 --> 00:10:37,000
Glasine o krizi su tu... Svetsko tržište
finansija je daleko ispod crte danas

161
00:10:37,001 --> 00:10:41,000
dramaticna dešavanja
za dva giganta sa Wall Street-a...

162
00:10:46,000 --> 00:10:48,800
Septembra 2008 godine

163
00:10:48,801 --> 00:10:52,000
bankrot americke investicione
banke Lehman Brothers

164
00:10:52,001 --> 00:10:53,500
i kolaps najvece svetske

165
00:10:53,501 --> 00:10:56,000
osiguravajuce kompanije AIG

166
00:10:56,001 --> 00:10:58,500
su izazvali globalnu finansijsku krizu

167
00:10:58,501 --> 00:10:59,700
...strah je zaledio tržišta preko noci

168
00:10:59,701 --> 00:11:01,300
sa krahom azijskih berzi...

169
00:11:01,301 --> 00:11:02,600
akcije se se sunovratile niz liticu

170
00:11:02,601 --> 00:11:05,400
najveci povezani krah u istoriji

171
00:11:05,401 --> 00:11:07,600
Cene deonica su nastavile sunovrat

172
00:11:07,601 --> 00:11:11,000
kao posledice kolapsa Lehmana

173
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,500
Rezultat je bio globalna recesija

174
00:11:14,501 --> 00:11:17,500
koja svet košta desetine triliona dolara,

175
00:11:17,501 --> 00:11:20,000
koja je ostavila 30 miliona ljudi bez posla

176
00:11:20,001 --> 00:11:23,500
i udvostrucila javni dug Amerike

177
00:11:23,501 --> 00:11:25,500
Ako hocete da izracunate cenu:

178
00:11:25,501 --> 00:11:28,500
strukturu otplacenog dela bogatstva,
stambenog bogatstva

179
00:11:28,501 --> 00:11:31,000
pa strukturu dohodaka, poslova,

180
00:11:31,001 --> 00:11:33,500
globalno gledano 15 miliona ljudi opet

181
00:11:33,501 --> 00:11:37,999
može da završi ispod granice siromaštva

182
00:11:38,000 --> 00:11:42,000
Ovo je ogromno skupa kriza

183
00:11:42,001 --> 00:11:45,000
Ova kriza nije slucajna

184
00:11:45,001 --> 00:11:48,500
Izazvala ju je industrija koja je
izvan kontrole

185
00:11:48,501 --> 00:11:52,000
Od 80-ih uspon americkog finansijskog sektora

186
00:11:52,001 --> 00:11:53,500
je doveo do serija

187
00:11:53,501 --> 00:11:57,000
žestokih finansijskih kriza

188
00:11:57,001 --> 00:12:00,000
Savaka kriza je donosila vecu štetu

189
00:12:00,001 --> 00:12:04,000
dok je industrija skupljala sve
više i više novca

190
00:12:05,000 --> 00:12:09,000
<b>DEO I. KAKO SMO OVDE DOSLI</b>

191
00:12:11,001 --> 00:12:14,200
Nakon velike depresije Amerika

192
00:12:14,201 --> 00:12:16,500
je imala 40 godina ekonomskog rasta

193
00:12:16,501 --> 00:12:19,002
bez i jedne finansijske krize

194
00:12:19,003 --> 00:12:22,000
finansijska industrija je bila
strogo regulisana

195
00:12:22,004 --> 00:12:24,400
uobicajene banke su bile lokalne poslovne

196
00:12:24,401 --> 00:12:26,500
i bile su im zabranjene spekulacije

197
00:12:26,501 --> 00:12:29,000
sa uštedjevinama ulagaca

198
00:12:29,001 --> 00:12:30,000
Investicione banke

199
00:12:30,001 --> 00:12:32,400
koje rade sa deonicama

200
00:12:32,401 --> 00:12:35,500
su bile mala partnerstva

201
00:12:35,501 --> 00:12:37,400
U tradicionalnim investicionim bankama

202
00:12:37,401 --> 00:12:39,300
po modelu partnerstva

203
00:12:39,301 --> 00:12:41,001
partneri ulažu taj novac i ocito oni

204
00:12:41,002 --> 00:12:42,754
Penzionisani profesor Investicionog Bankarstva
Harvard Business School

205
00:12:43,001 --> 00:12:45,000
paze taj novac jako oprezno

206
00:12:45,001 --> 00:12:46,700
Hteli bi da žive lepo

207
00:12:46,701 --> 00:12:48,000
ali ne bi hteli da

208
00:12:48,001 --> 00:12:49,500
da rizikuju sve bez osnova

209
00:12:49,501 --> 00:12:53,000
Paul Vocker je radio u odeljenju trezora

210
00:12:53,001 --> 00:12:54,300
i bio je predsednik Federalnih Rezervi

211
00:12:54,301 --> 00:12:57,800
od 1979 do 1987

212
00:12:57,801 --> 00:12:59,500
pre nego je ušao u vladu,

213
00:12:59,501 --> 00:13:01,300
bio je finansijski ekonomista

214
00:13:01,301 --> 00:13:03,000
u banci  Chase Manhattan

215
00:13:03,001 --> 00:13:08,001
kad sam napustio Chase zbog trezora 1969

216
00:13:08,002 --> 00:13:10,300
Mislim da sam imao dohodak od oko

217
00:13:10,301 --> 00:13:13,400
45000 dolara godišnje

218
00:13:13,400 --> 00:13:16,500
Morgan Stanley je 1972

219
00:13:16,501 --> 00:13:21,500
je ukupno imao 110 zaposlenih

220
00:13:21,501 --> 00:13:26,013
Jednu kancelariju i kapital od
12 miliona dolara

221
00:13:26,014 --> 00:13:31,000
Sada Morgan Stanley ima 50 000 radnika,

222
00:13:31,001 --> 00:13:36,000
nekoliko milijardi kapitala i

223
00:13:36,001 --> 00:13:38,000
kancelarije širom sveta

224
00:13:38,001 --> 00:13:41,015
80-ih je industrija finansija eksplodirala

225
00:13:41,500 --> 00:13:43,500
Investicione banke su se otvorile

226
00:13:43,501 --> 00:13:47,000
